---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "About — Class6Loaner";
const description =
  "Why Class6Loaner exists: a safety-first community project that evolved from solving a practical road-test problem into a mentorship-first process.";
const canonicalPath = "/about";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath={canonicalPath}>
  <section class="card">
    <h1 style="margin:0 0 10px; font-weight:1000;">About Class6Loaner</h1>

    <p class="muted" style="max-width:95ch; margin:0 0 10px;">
      Class6Loaner started with a simple, practical problem: many new riders can book a Class 6 road test,
      but don’t have reliable access to a <strong>road-test-ready motorcycle</strong> on the right day — and time slots can be limited.
    </p>

    <p class="muted" style="max-width:95ch; margin:0 0 10px;">
      Over time, something bigger became obvious. A short amount of calm, experience-based guidance before test day
      (through messaging, checklists, and clear expectations) can help a test-taker show up prepared and reduce anxiety.
    </p>

    <p class="muted" style="max-width:95ch; margin:0 0 10px;">
      Just as important: when experienced riders consistently push a <strong>safety-first mindset</strong>,
      new riders are more likely to pace themselves, respect their limits, and build confidence responsibly.
      That carries into their first season — and helps them find the right riding partners and habits.
    </p>

    <div class="card" style="padding:14px; margin-top:12px;">
      <div style="font-weight:1000;">What Class6Loaner is (and isn’t)</div>
      <ul class="muted" style="margin:10px 0 0; max-width:95ch;">
        <li><strong>Is:</strong> structured Class 6 road-test support, focused on preparation, coordination, and accountability.</li>
        <li><strong>Is not:</strong> a joyride rental marketplace, and not a riding school or lesson platform.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="muted" style="margin-top:12px; display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/how-it-works">How it works →</a>
      <a href="/mentor-guide">Mentor guide →</a>
      <a href="/road-test-guide">Test-taker guide →</a>
      <a href="https://borrowmybike.ca/legal#damage" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Damage &amp; responsibility →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
